00:16:50.270 --> 00:16:51.270
Magkarera tayo.

00:16:53.920 --> 00:16:54.850
Hindi interesado.

00:16:55.260 --> 00:16:56.530
Narinig ko na si Jiang Mu

00:16:56.680 --> 00:16:58.150
magtatanghal sa isang palabas pangkawanggawa

00:16:58.150 --> 00:17:00.190
kasama si Nana ngayong gabi.

00:17:00.470 --> 00:17:04.230
Gawin nating
finish line ang entertainment center.

00:17:04.560 --> 00:17:07.160
Sinumang unang makarating doon
ay magdiriwang kasama niya;

00:17:07.339 --> 00:17:08.800
at kung sino man ang dumating mamaya

00:17:09.190 --> 00:17:11.400
hindi na sasama sa buhay niya at hindi na muling magpapakita
sa harap niya.

00:17:11.400 --> 00:17:12.530
Ano ang tunog niyan?

00:17:15.599 --> 00:17:17.710
Napaka-interesante niyang babae.

00:17:17.950 --> 00:17:19.430
Gusto mo siya?

00:17:23.750 --> 00:17:24.550
Sumakay ka sa kotse.

00:17:31.680 --> 00:17:33.880
Magsuot ka ng earphones at huwag mong ibaba ang telepono.

00:17:37.030 --> 00:17:39.090
May iba pa bang mga patakaran?
Sabihin mo lahat nang sabay-sabay.

00:17:40.320 --> 00:17:41.360
